<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">There can&apos;t be any connection--there can&apos;t be any comparison. Harry Potter may be what youngsters like, but The Glass Bead Game surpasses those books <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">There can't be any connection--there can't be any comparison. Harry Potter may be what youngsters like, but The Glass Bead Game surpasses those books a million times.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
